{"tid":2012020,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(攬炒全書懶人包) 全民拎綜援 政府冇銀用","createTime":"2020-05-11T11:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T23:26:20.000Z","uid":326037,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d5feb6020d2e9e0bbeaff066f633396bd9e80fb7","tid":2012020,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T11:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HJbGLef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHJbGLef.png&h=62fdd68e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府冇銀用 一籌莫展<br />\n<br />\n用盡每一個方法駛政府錢拉挎政府財政，<span style=\"color: red;\">有機會/合資格拎綜援的人可以試下申請</span> 唔駛再怕人嫌棄<br />\n<br />\n搞到政府冇錢先係攬炒主要目標，冇錢就冇能力推行反人權的政治理念<br />\n<br />\n(攬炒公務員)政府冇錢比人工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2009167/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2009167/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒國企藍店)永續黃圈 民主消費<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2001434/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2001434/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒銀行)唔夠美金 大陸金融有流動性陷阱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2000285/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2000285/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒流動支付)唔用支付寶吸唔到香港人血<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1979144/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1979144/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒金融流動性)冇美金印唔到錢借唔到出去救經濟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1439205/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1439205/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒人民幣)數碼人民幣買唔到外國貨只能國內消費<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2008253/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2008253/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n(反攻香港)建立海外武裝反政兼逃生 養流亡義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2007554/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2007554/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒經濟)數碼經濟轉型 反送中生機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2003600/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2003600/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒外史)全球最大全民抗極權經驗 波蘭反共運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2009192/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2009192/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"52dd0b776c3a823d2b2ae72a29ab65d10c773ac6","tid":2012020,"uid":7149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:40:49.000Z","msg":"唔係藍絲 但你掏空政府庫房 比大鱷黎香港洗錢 到時香港真係玩完 政治都唔撚得閒搞"},{"pid":"2286eeddfdf3589f2843132f3ffe7161f318715a","tid":2012020,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"52dd0b776c3a823d2b2ae72a29ab65d10c773ac6","tid":2012020,"uid":7149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:40:49.000Z","msg":"唔係藍絲 但你掏空政府庫房 比大鱷黎香港洗錢 到時香港真係玩完 政治都唔撚得閒搞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:44:15.000Z","msg":"外匯基金不等於財政儲備"},{"pid":"dade45addebe9ab648f2ea42eec51e159034eba4","tid":2012020,"uid":325263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:24:17.000Z","msg":"到時大陸鳩黎買晒香港人啲資產你就pk <br />\n<br />\n到時你唔想奶共都要奶"},{"pid":"674c22f716ab249846538a9afbeff790acbcb975","tid":2012020,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dade45addebe9ab648f2ea42eec51e159034eba4","tid":2012020,"uid":325263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:24:17.000Z","msg":"到時大陸鳩黎買晒香港人啲資產你就pk <br />\n<br />\n到時你唔想奶共都要奶"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:33:30.000Z","msg":"大陸已經買晒啦，你仲有咩資產未比大陸人買?"},{"pid":"2dbb997d844f474fdf9800f02c33c98c97fbe73e","tid":2012020,"uid":325263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"674c22f716ab249846538a9afbeff790acbcb975","tid":2012020,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dade45addebe9ab648f2ea42eec51e159034eba4","tid":2012020,"uid":325263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:24:17.000Z","msg":"到時大陸鳩黎買晒香港人啲資產你就pk <br />\n<br />\n到時你唔想奶共都要奶"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:33:30.000Z